: \"Dreams will be achieved, hopes dashed, careers defined andlegacies cementedwith the eyes of the world on events such asNoah Lyles' hunt for 100m sprint gold, a three-way battle for the women's 100m medals,Josh Kerr and Jakob Ingebritsen's tussle for 1500m glory, orSimone Biles' return to the Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9936396393205217, \"rank\": 0.003993892002624156, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999733973, \"rank\": 2.119494346964772e-11, \"text\": \"Jakob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But whilemany athletes arrive in the prime of their careers, with years of experienced blended with three years of preparation, what about those who are just starting out, or those in the twilight end of their careers?\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese skateboarder Zheng Haohao will be the youngest competitor at the Games, at the age of just 11 years and 11 months when she competes in the park event.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9755770751307729, \"rank\": 0.024626791110342806, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9908465027655508, \"rank\": 0.006817703796424